    excerpt: { es: "El SEO es el canal de marketing más rentable a largo plazo para tu negocio de alquiler vacacional. Keyword research, SEO on-page, técnico, local y link building explicados paso a paso.", en: "SEO is the most profitable long-term marketing channel for your vacation rental business. Keyword research, on-page, technical, local SEO and link building explained step by step." },
