    slug: { es: "calcular-comisiones-airbnb-booking", en: "calculate-airbnb-booking-commissions" },
    title: { es: "Calculadora: cuánto pierdes realmente en comisiones de Airbnb y Booking", en: "Calculator: how much you really lose in Airbnb and Booking commissions" },
    excerpt: { es: "Desglose real de las comisiones de Airbnb, Booking.com y VRBO con cálculos concretos para carteras de 10, 30 y 50 propiedades. Descubre cuánto ahorrarías con reservas directas.", en: "Real breakdown of Airbnb, Booking.com and VRBO commissions with concrete calculations for portfolios of 10, 30 and 50 properties. Discover how much you'd save with direct bookings." },
    date: "2026-03-10",
