    title: { es: "Channel manager vs motor de reservas: qué necesitas realmente y por qué no es lo mismo", en: "Channel manager vs booking engine: what you really need and why they are not the same" },
    excerpt: { es: "Muchos gestores confunden channel manager con motor de reservas. Son herramientas distintas con funciones complementarias. Te explicamos cuál necesitas, cuándo usar un todo-en-uno y cómo elegir según tu cartera.", en: "Many managers confuse channel managers with booking engines. They are different tools with complementary functions. We explain which one you need, when an all-in-one works, and how to choose based on your portfolio size." },
